==Russian==

===Indefinite pronoun===
'''[[кто]]-[[либо]]''' (któ-libo)
:'''N.B.''' &mdash; the particle -[[либо]] imparts a stronger sense of indefiniteness than [[-то]] or [[-нибудь]].

# [[anybody]], [[anyone]], [[somebody]], [[someone]]
#:*{{RUchar|[[если|е́сли]] кто́-либо [[об]] [[этот|э́том]] [[узнавать|узна́ет]]...}} — ''if anybody should find out about this...''

